AttributeList.Text: Check balance tank level, feedback correct on V01.13, V01.14, V01.04. Load temp set point for pre-rinse and transfer to regulator. Regulator to auto. Open steam supply valve 01.58. Start circulation pump 01.39. Open route to spray ball through V01.03. Start delay open timer V01.12. Step on.

If pre-rinse timer has expired, reset V01.014 (route to rec-irculate), set V01.13 ready to pulse, step on.
Check to see if chemical dosing is already active. Load temp set point for caustic and request caustic dosing. Step on.
